<p><a href="../../GovPubs/gao/gao25.htm">Juvenile Justice:
Juveniles Processed In Criminal Court and Case Dispositions </a>(Letter
Report, 08/15/95, GAO/GGD-95-170).</p>

<p><a href="../../GovPubs/gao/gao26.htm">Juvenile Justice:
