<h2><font size="6">Richardson-Taylor Reunion News </font></h2>

<p>Every year, the Richardson-Taylor clan holds a family reunion
to celebrate something or other -- no one is really sure. For a
variety of reasons, I have been selected to write the newsletter
for the annual reunion. Listed below are the reunion newsletters
from years past. </p>

